{
  "key": 18355,
  "messages": [
    {
      "id": "SnowpointCity_Text_OnlyChosenMayEnterTemple",
      "en_US": [
        "Only the chosen may enter\n",
        "the Snowpoint Temple.\r",
        "I’m sorry, but you will have to\n",
        "leave.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SnowpointCity_Text_OnlyChosenMayEnterTemple2",
      "en_US": [
        "Only the chosen may enter\n",
        "the Snowpoint Temple.\r",
        "I’m sorry, but you will have to\n",
        "leave."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SnowpointCity_Text_BuiltInAncientTimes",
      "en_US": [
        "The temple is said to have been\n",
        "built in ancient times.\r",
        "It pays homage to the Pokémon of rock,\n",
        "ice, and steel that shape the land.\r",
        "So it is told."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SnowpointCity_Text_LetThatPersonIn",
      "en_US": [
        "Candice: It’s OK!\n",
        "You can let that person in.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SnowpointCity_Text_EnjoyYourExploring",
      "en_US": [
        "I heard from Cynthia.\r",
        "You’re working on a Pokédex,\n",
        "aren’t you?\r",
        "There should be many rare Pokémon\n",
        "in the temple.\r",
        "Enjoy your exploring!"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SnowpointCity_Text_TownIsFreezingCold",
      "en_US": [
        "Brrr... This snowbound town is always\n",
        "freezing cold.\r",
        "But the spirits of the Trainers and\n",
        "their Pokémon burn hot and bright.\r",
        "Especially the Gym Leader."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SnowpointCity_Text_ScarfLooksWarm",
      "en_US": [
        "Your scarf looks nice and warm.\n",
        "I wish I had one like it."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SnowpointCity_Text_IWantToLookAroundTemple",
      "en_US": [
        "I want to take a look around in the\n",
        "Snowpoint Temple.\r",
        "But only really tough Trainers are\n",
        "allowed inside."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SnowpointCity_Text_PokemonDraggedCityHere",
      "en_US": [
        "Pokémon are said to have dragged\n",
        "Snowpoint City here.\r",
        "The Snowpoint Temple is their resting\n",
        "place, they say."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SnowpointCity_Text_CandiceIsTeachingMe",
      "en_US": [
        "Candice is teaching me about Pokémon.\r",
        "She says I have to start by making\n",
        "friends with Pokémon."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SnowpointCity_Text_SailToBattleZone",
      "en_US": [
        "What is it? Do you want to sail\n",
        "to the Battle Zone?"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SnowpointCity_Text_LetsSetSail",
      "en_US": [
        "Aye, aye, then!\n",
        "Let’s set sail!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SnowpointCity_Text_YouCantGoUsingSurf",
      "en_US": [
        "What is it?\n",
        "The Battle Zone’s rough to get to.\r",
        "The sea around it is always roiling\n",
        "with choppy waves.\r",
        "You can’t go there using Surf,\n",
        "that’s for sure."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SnowpointCity_Text_ILookForwardToAGreatTrainer",
      "en_US": [
        "Hey kid! Looking to head to\n",
        "the Battle Zone?\r",
        "Candice, the gym leader here in\n",
        "Snowpoint City, deems who is capable\f",
        "of taking the area on.\r",
        "Get her gym badge and try again!"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SnowpointCity_Text_NothingExceptionalHere",
      "en_US": [
        "There is nothing exceptional here.\n",
        "That makes Snowpoint unique.\r",
        "There’s nothing exceptional about me.\n",
        "That’s what makes me stand out!"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SnowpointCity_Text_ImGladIWaited",
      "en_US": [
        "Cynthia: I thought you would come.\n",
        "It’s good to see you!\r",
        "I wanted to thank you for helping\n",
        "my grandmother with Team Galactic\f",
        "back in Celestic Town.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SnowpointCity_Text_GoodThatOurWorldChanges",
      "en_US": [
        "Cynthia: She informed me of that man.\r",
        "Cyrus...\r",
        "I don’t think I have to be the one\n",
        "to tell you that the world he envisions\f",
        "is a foolish one...\r",
        "But still, the threat he poses is all\n",
        "too real.\r",
        "The kind of world I want to see is where\n",
        "everyone can share their joy.\r",
        "Where Pokémon and the people around\n",
        "them can be happy for each other.\r",
        "I want the world to become a place\n",
        "where everyone is smiling.\r",
        "The world could be so much better\n",
        "if we all tried to make it that way.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SnowpointCity_Text_TravelToFarOffPlaces",
      "en_US": [
        "I want you to keep traveling to many\n",
        "far-off places.\r",
        "I want you to keep meeting all kinds of\n",
        "people and Pokémon.\r",
        "Steel your resolve such that if you are\n",
        "to encounter him again, our world will\f",
        "have a steadfast defender.\r",
        "Your horizons will expand again if you\n",
        "visit the Fight Area as well.\r",
        "I hope our paths cross again!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SnowpointCity_Text_MapSign",
      "en_US": [
        "Snowpoint City\n",
        "City of Snow"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "SnowpointCity_Text_SignPokemonGym",
      "en_US": [
        "Snowpoint City Pokémon Gym\n",
        "Leader: Candice\f",
        "The Diamond Dust Girl!"
      ]
    }
  ]
}
